text.tspan: My primary role here was teaching English to native Korean speakers. I taught various age
groups, and skill levels. Designing creative lesson plans and classroom management played a
key role in providing a productive learning environment for students. Outside of the classroom I
was a liaison to foreign teachers from the U.S. and abroad.
